  53:src/engine.cpp **** // Shared reverb â€” one instance, fed by whichever voice has a reverb_send. Its
  54:src/engine.cpp **** // ~66 KB of delay lines live in static storage (zero-initialised = silent). HF
  55:src/engine.cpp **** // damping is fixed for now; tail length / level are the global g_reverb_* params.
